to the people of Tajikistan in their efforts to restore peace,
stability and civic accord in the republic."
</P>
<P>
The Russian president also expressed condolences to the
families of those killed.
</P>
<P>
Two people were killed and 49 wounded in the grenade attack
today. Rakhmonov suffered a minor leg injury. 
</P>
</TEXT>
