<HEADLINE> Pak President Arrives in Islamabad After </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, April 30 (Xinhua) - Pakistani President Farooq
Leghari arrived here today after ending a two-day working visit to
China.
</P>
<P>
During his visit from April 29 to 30, Leghari held talks with
his Chinese counterpart Jiang Zemin, Chinese Premier Li Peng and
other senior Chinese trade and commercial officials.
</P>
