The 21st meeting of the Standing Committee of the CPPCC's
Eighth National Committee will be held here in late June,
according to a decision made at today's meeting.
</P>
<P>
The scheduled meeting will focus on Deng Xiaoping's exposition
on the people's political consultation.  
