political nature."
</P>
<P>
The incident took place this morning in the northern city of
Khudjand when the president and leaders of the city and region
were getting out of their cars at a theatre to attend the
celebrations of the 65th anniversary of Khudjand University.
</P>
<P>
At least two other officials were wounded but there were no
reports of any deaths in the attack.
</P>
<P>
The Itar-Tass news agency said that a suspect, identified as
20-year-old Firdavs Dustboboyev, has been detained.
</P>
<P>
