<HEADLINE> Xinhua Stock Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 30 (Xinhua) -- Today's Xinhua A stock index
gained 3.27 points to close at 196.43, while the Xinhua B stock
index was up by 2.26 points to finish at 101.01.
</P>
<P>
The Xinhua stock index is China's first national unitary stock
exponent, which is jointly designed and issued by the Economic
Information Department of Xinhua News Agency and Beijing
University. 
</P>
</TEXT>
